  • Classes in ge.vakho.gxt used by ge.vakho.gxt
    Class
    Description
    Block1
    TKEY Block (also knows as Block 1) consists of the block information and TKEY entries.
    Block2
    TDAT Block (also knows as Block 2) consists of the block information and TDAT entries.
    GXT
    GXT consists of two blocks: Block1 and Block2 blocks.
    TDAT
    TDAT contains the value string that is an array of wide characters (2 bytes per character) to be displayed in the game.
    TKEY
    TKEY block contains TDAT entry offset and its name.
